  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="container my-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>
        <p>
          Gubbachi Crop Sciences, based in Bangalore, India, is a pioneering biotechnology company providing <strong>cost-effective and high-quality genetic testing services</strong> to the seed industry. With over <strong>25 years of molecular biology expertise</strong>, we specialize in <strong>genotyping, hybrid seed support, inbred line development, and molecular marker-assisted selection (MAS)</strong> to accelerate breeding cycles and improve crop traits.
        </p>
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>
          Our mission is to harness the power of biotechnology to provide <strong>economical and precise testing solutions</strong> that support the agricultural sector in developing high-yield, disease-resistant, and climate-resilient crops.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

